@ljharb to possibly help with the time pressure, if you do decide to go for allowing the `"∞"` string, the [schema](https://github.com/benmosher/eslint-plugin-import/blob/296262842b52a50c5b107ba91bb2d13c05b2a104/src/rules/no-cycle.js#L17-L21) may end up looking something like

```
      maxDepth:{
        description: 'maximum dependency depth to traverse',
        type: ['integer', 'string'],
        minimum: 1,
        pattern: "^∞$",
      },
```
